<module>
    <h>ceàrr</h>
    <p><g>ceàrr</g>
        <en>wrong</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <module id="gille">
            <h>gille</h>
            <p><g>ceàrr air <a href="?gd=gille">gille</a></g>
                <en>wrong with a boy</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dé tha ceàrr air a’ ghille seo? Tha a cheann goirt.</gd>
                        <tr>What is wrong with this boy? His head is sore.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <module id="glais">
            <h>glais</h>
            <p>
                <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha rudeigin ceàrr air a’ ghlais seo.</gd>
                        <tr>Something is wrong with this lock.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 41</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>




